REQUIREMENTS
------------

	Qt6
	Qwt (compiled against Qt6)
	SDL
	glew
	boost
	

BUILDING
--------
	cd build
	./compile-release.sh [threads]

RUNNING
-------
	./src/bengine app_critterding
	./src/bengine app_critterding_threads (experimental)

KEYS
----
	F1      open admin window
	F2      open control panel
	F3      open system monitor

	up      move forward
	down    move backwards
	left    move left
	right   move right
	home    move up
	end     move down

	[4]     look left
	[5]     look right
	[8]     look down
	[2]     look up
	[1]     tilt left
	[3]     tilt right

MOUSE
-----
	button 2    entity admin window
	button 3    grab critter / food

bobke...
